{"tid":1357392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急][幫推]熱門資訊太混亂，上環元朗都重要，求開上環/元朗台，或頂置重要資訊/整合/運動Post","createTime":"2019-07-23T17:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T19:00:53.000Z","uid":20024,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2fef64e089b04aa5877bbf606a28f1da00777e49","tid":1357392,"uid":20024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:03:41.000Z","msg":"資訊混亂會嚴重影響運動安排及進展，<br />\n<br />\n同意請比意見/推/like，感謝大家"},{"pid":"410317fd0f2ec8f93ca96be92c3395711f5feff8","tid":1357392,"uid":20024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:05:35.000Z","msg":"拋磚引玉，希望大家討論吓不同意見既成效<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1. 短期內舉辦光復元朗行動<br />\n<br />\n2. 搜集任何相關資料，包括但不限有關人仕個人資料，相關物業/店舖資料，活躍地點，行蹤等等<br />\n<br />\n<del>3. 透過海關，入境，警方，食環等等相關部門，清洗元朗黃賭毒產業鏈 ，烏煙瘴氣</del><span style=\"color: red;\">好多巴打覺得警黑合作，成效不大</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 眾籌去聘請例如G4S/黑水等國際保安公司，保護各議員，知名人仕如陳伯，記者們，其他有需要市民等等<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">好多巴打贊成呢個方案</span><br />\n<br />\n5. 元朗放盤/退租，警黑合作，治安全無<br />\n<br />\n6. 舉報僭建<br />\n<br />\n7. 全民對抗新鴻基SHK運動<br />\n<br />\n8. 而家鄉黑最搵錢嘅係貨櫃場同倉，要斷就要諗辦法斷米路</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n[集思廣益]發夢夢到殲滅元朗官商鄉黑計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1342215\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1342215</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[發夢][眾籌]聘請G4S/黑水保護議員，記者，陳伯，市民等是否可行？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1343417\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1343417</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n[發夢][不合作][長期]元朗放盤/退租行動，考慮吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345525</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n廣州人仕開始進場，大家小心注意風向<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1349432\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1349432</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"dc7510210ca7a81ea29588acee6087bef33e8a9c","tid":1357392,"uid":31719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:06:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持全民戴頭盔搭地鐵返工</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">屌你罷工罷課 你地唔夠膽<br />\n咁帶個頭盔返工得喇掛 咁都做唔到<br />\n唔戴住係頭 都扣係個袋喇</span>"},{"pid":"dddf4a15b7d03401fd341c1fa728486fcd27cbcc","tid":1357392,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:06:45.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d8571e7f5a7306311df3796cdcd9a65be8b5a1e","tid":1357392,"uid":237077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nBtCFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nBtCFX.jpg&h=a3d5aa01&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"59e93c82b4107324b651a252dfdb2f9e13a71b7e","tid":1357392,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"想問 有冇議員追問被防最吞左既義士？<br />\n同埋中頭既手足 有冇情報？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f108c891aa77c1d7d8fd7f43bbad4d3415491eac","tid":1357392,"uid":20024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59e93c82b4107324b651a252dfdb2f9e13a71b7e","tid":1357392,"uid":102378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"想問 有冇議員追問被防最吞左既義士？<br />\n同埋中頭既手足 有冇情報？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:14:36.000Z","msg":"暫時未睇到相關資訊，我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />太亂"},{"pid":"297cf579d7d8a558f39beb6e276452110278d2d0","tid":1357392,"uid":20024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:20:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3d5eb53ef241eb65e3d132fb8a7d31f8f70b376f","tid":1357392,"uid":20024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T17:43:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc00b2a1a19cdff8646aeb78701ad92abf364136","tid":1357392,"uid":2002